getDateConverterForGraphs

public CalendarConverter getDateConverterForGraphs()
gets a CalendarConverter which is derived from the normal CalendarConverter, but without the year. To be used for cewolf graphs as Strings along the x-axis, where normal date labels with a year would be to long and make the x-axis too packed with labels.

Returns:
a CalendarConverter without the year.
